      <title>研究显示，气候变化将使非洲 GDP 减少 7.1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/climate-change-to-slash-african-gdp-by-7-1-study-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的研究显示，气候变化将导致 2 亿非洲人陷入严重饥饿，农作物收入减少 30%，人均国内生产总值减少 7.1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/climate-change-to-slash-african-gdp-by-7-1-study-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:15:52 GMT</pubDate>
